column14: There is a healthy relationship between canine breeders and small animal (general practice) veterinarians.
column15: There is a community need for purebred and purpose bred dogs.
column16: There is adequate educational material provided on canine breeding and whelping in the current Tufts pre-clinical curriculum.
column17: After graduation, I intend to practice in small animal (general practice) medicine with extensive canine breeder clientele.
column18: I feel confident graduating from Tufts and practicing in small animal (general practice) medicine with extensive canine breeder clientele.
